# Tkinter UI

## Layout

- Main window: 1200×800 dashboard with **Today's Log** bar (8 quick-log buttons + fitness), category cards, Recent Activity panel.
- Fitness Hub: grouped program tree (expandable step series) + Step Detail panel with demo video link; search bar filters programs/steps.
- All list/dialog windows: mouse-wheel scroll via `ui_scroll.py`.
- Footer actions: Refresh, View Full History, **Graphs & Summaries**, Settings.
- Log dialog: 540×720 modal with rating spinbox, checklist, metrics, scrolled notes.

## Patterns

- Use `ttk.Frame`, `ttk.Label`, `ttk.Button`, `ttk.Notebook` for tabs.
- Modal dialogs: `transient(root)`, `grab_set()`, destroy on save/cancel.
- `ScrolledText` for notes, history, and summary tab.
- Category cards show: name, category streak, today's status (green if logged).

## Graphs & Summaries Window

- `ttk.Notebook` with **Summaries** (text) and **Graphs** (embedded matplotlib) tabs.
- Summaries: Today, This Week (7d), Last 30 Days — avg rating, active days, notes count, streaks.
- Graphs: 30-day daily avg line chart; all-time per-category bar chart.

## Style

- Central theme: `ui_theme.py` — colors, fonts, ttk styles, card helpers, text widget styling.
- Apply on startup via `ui_theme.apply_theme(root)`; use `configure_window()` on Toplevel dialogs.
- Palette: soft gray background, white cards, teal accent (`#2F7A7B`), amber streak badge.
- Category cards: colored left accent stripe per life area (`CATEGORY_ACCENTS`).
- Button styles: `Accent.TButton` (primary), `Logged.TButton` (completed today), default `TButton`.
- Streak color: `#D97706`. Logged today: `#059669`. Not logged: muted gray.
- Font: Segoe UI on Windows, Helvetica elsewhere.
